### ID del villano creado
@villanoId = {{createVillano.response.body.data.id}}

### PUT actualizar villano
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/villanos/{{villanoId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Victor Von Doom",
  "alias": "Doctor Doom",
  "origen": "Latveria",
  "telefono": "+1-555-0123",
  "mail": "doom@latveria.com",
  "nivelPeligrosidad": "Alto",
  "motivacion": "Dominio mundial y venganza contra Reed Richards",
  "estado": "activo",
